                                      "type": "intrinsic",
                                    },
                                  },
                                  {
                                    "comment": {
                                      "shortText": "The verification status of the factor, default is \`unverified\` after \`.enroll()\`, then \`verified\` after the user verifies it with \`.verify()\`",
